        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-什么是JVM"><a href="#1-什么是JVM" class="headerlink" title="1. 什么是JVM"></a>1. 什么是JVM</h2><p><img src="https://hexo-1304867193.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/images/image-20260705145041732.png" alt="image-20260705145041732"></p><h2 id="2-运行时数据区"><a href="#2-运行时数据区" class="headerlink" title="2. 运行时数据区"></a>2. 运行时数据区</h2><h3 id="1-程序计数器"><a href="#1-程序计数器" class="headerlink" title="1. 程序计数器"></a>1. 程序计数器</h3><p><img src="https://hexo-1304867193.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/images/image-20260705145052850.png" alt="image-20260705145052850"></p><h3 id="2-JVM-栈"><a href="#2-JVM-栈" class="headerlink" title="2. JVM 栈"></a>2. JVM 栈</h3><p><img src="https://hexo-1304867193.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/images/image-20260705145102783.png" alt="image-20260705145102783"></p><h3 id="3-堆"><a href="#3-堆" class="headerlink" title="3. 堆"></a>3. 堆</h3><p><img src="https://hexo-1304867193.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/images/image-20260705145114131.png" alt="image-20260705145114131"></p>]]></content>
      
      
